b'Biometric #authN is the \xe2\x80\x9csomething you are\xe2\x80\x9d factor of #MFA (Ex fingerprint or facial recognition) but it\xe2\x80\x99s not a security panacea #ChatSTC'
b'Factors can be something you know (ex: PIN), something you have (mobile phone), and something you are (your fingerprint) #ChatSTC'
b'Your information is safe because thieves would need to steal both your password and your phone, for example, to log in #ChatSTC'
b'#MFA helps protect you by adding an additional layer of security, making it harder for bad guys to log in as if they were you #ChatSTC'
b'Many websites now offer #MFA options (sometimes called two-factor authentication) \xe2\x80\x93 see a list of them at https://t.co/pLtZu8yseb #ChatSTC'
b'We recognize that passwords have been a doorway to many breaches. #MFA\xe2\x80\x99s gaining traction bc it\xe2\x80\x99s easy & adds a layer of security #ChatSTC'
b'In 2015, 63% of confirmed data breaches involved leveraging weak/default/stolen passwords - @Verizon https://t.co/q4Cq32a7CD #ChatSTC'
b'#MFA is a #security enhancement where you present two pieces of evidence to log in to an account \xe2\x80\x93 adding a 2nd layer of security #ChatSTC'
b'You\xe2\x80\x99ve used #MFA before if you\xe2\x80\x99ve swiped a bank card then entered your PIN at the ATM \xe2\x80\x93 you\xe2\x80\x99re using two factors to gain access #ChatSTC'
b'Use longer passphrases instead of passwords. They\xe2\x80\x99re easier to remember but harder to crack! #ChatSTC'
b'Always add a second layer of security to your account by turning on multi-factor authentication #MFA #authN #ChatSTC'
b'For us, #PasswordDay isn\xe2\x80\x99t just about better password practices - it\xe2\x80\x99s about better passwords & securing accts w/ #MFA! #ChatSTC'
b'When people find passwords difficult to use & remember, they make them easy to remember + repeat them across multiple accounts #ChatSTC'

b'Long term: Consumer will bring own #MFA rather than having it issued; think BYOD for auth. Also, consumers begin to expect it. #ChatSTC'
b'Long term: expect more security & choice as #MFA & strong auth becomes the norm. #ChatSTC'
b'Near: We\xe2\x80\x99ll see a reduction in breach incidents due to passwords #ChatSTC'

b'@USAA offers 3 options: facial, voice (2 informed by #NSTIC pilot @DaonInc), & fingerprint. ~400,000 customers have opted in. #ChatSTC'
b'Facial, voice, and fingerprint biometrics are some factors that #NSTIC pilots are currently exploring and implementing #ChatSTC'
b'Benefits= ubiquity due to mobility. Trends= biometric can never leave the device-meaning it can\xe2\x80\x99t be stolen. #ChatSTC'
b'All #ChatSTC partners today are affecting global adoption. #NSTIC pilots are also working on solutions that can have a global impact.'

b'#NSTIC incentivizes industry adoption through a collaborative approach & our 3 pillars: pilots, IDESG, + http://t.co/sthY9AAbp6 #ChatSTC'
b'We\xe2\x80\x99re happy that stronger authentication is a trend! At #NSTIC, pilots are exploring trends in biometrics and testing new ideas #ChatSTC'
b'Proof once. Issue Once. Federate. Use everywhere. And privacy is key. #ChatSTC'
b'MFA is a win-win: businesses save $ that would be lost in redress after a breach and show concern for security of consumers\xe2\x80\x99 data #ChatSTC'

b'Both. #NSTIC envisions a collaborative effort, where businesses offer strong auth methods like #MFA and consumers choose to adopt. #ChatSTC'
b'#NSTIC pilot #MFA options include: fingerprint and facial biometrics, picture password, SMS/text, email, and phone call #ChatSTC'
b'Options today include P/W, token, ID badge, crypto key, & biometrics. #NSTIC pilots are developing + deploying 10 #MFA solutions #ChatSTC'
b'Enabling MFA enhances online trust, security, & privacy. It lets us do things online in a very safe way. #ChatSTC'
b'MFA is how we need to authenticate, which = increased confidence in transactions; check http://t.co/pLtZu8yseb to see who offers it #ChatSTC'
b'MFA is multiple factors to prove you are actually you when logging in, like PIN (something u know) + smartcard (something you have) #ChatSTC'
b'The administration uses #MFA. Users authenticate w/ 2 or more factors to conduct transactions, strengthening security. #ChatSTC'
